\c 36
\s Kurwa kwaSani-Heribhi neJerusarema
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvichaitika, mugore regumi nemana ramambo Hezekia, Sani-Heribhi mambo weAsiriya wakakwira kurwisa maguta ese aJudha akashoshewa, ndokuatora.
\v 2 Zvino mambo weAsiriya wakatuma Rabhi-Shake kubva paRakishi kuenda kuJerusarema kuna mambo Hezekiya ane hondo huru. Zvino wakamira pamugero wedziva riri pamusoro, panzira huru yemunda wemusuki.
\v 3 Zvino kwakabudira kwaari Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikiya, waiva pamusoro peimba \add yamambo\add*, naShebhina munyori, naJoa mwanakomana waAsafi, munyoro wenhoroondo.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Rabhi-Shake wakati kwavari: Itii henyu kuna Hezekia: Anoreva seizvi mambo, mambo weAsiriya: Chivimboi ichi chaunovimba nacho?
\v 5 Ndinoti (asi ishoko remiromo): Kune zano nesimba rehondo, zvino ikozvino unovimba nani kuti undimukire?
\v 6 Tarira, unovimba nemudonzvo werutsanga urwu rwakavhunika, neEgipita, irwo munhu akazembera parwuri rwunopinda muruoko rwake ndokurwubaya, wakadaro Farao kune vanovimba naye.
\v 7 Asi kana uchiti kwandiri: Tinovimba naJehovha Mwari wedu, ko haasi iye nzvimbo dzka dzakakwirira nedziaritari dzake Hezekia zvaakabvisa ndokuti kuna Judha neJerusarema: Muchakotamira pamberi pearitari iyi here?
\v 8 Naizvozvo zvino chipa hako chibatiso kuna tenzi wangu, mambo weAsiriya, zvino ndichakupa mabhiza zvuru zviviri, kana iwe uchigona kupa vatasvi vemabhiza pamusoro pawo.
\v 9 Uchadzosera sei chiso chemutongi umwe wemudikisa wevaranda vatenzi wangu? Ugoisa chivimbo chako kuEgipita pangoro nevatasvi vemabhiza?
\v 10 Ikozvino ndakwira here ndisina Jehovha kurwisa nyika iyi kuiparadza.
\p
\v 11 Zvino Eriyakimu naShebha naJowa vakati kuna Rabhi-Shake: Taura hako kuvaranda vako muChiaramiya, nokuti tino\add chi\add*nzwisisa; uye musataura kwatiri ChiJudha, munzeve dzevanhu vese vari parusvingo.
\v 12 Asi Rabhi-Shake wakati: Tenzi wangu akandituma kuna tenzi wako nekwauri here, kutaura mashoko awa? Hakusi kuvanhu vagere parusvingo here kuti vadye ndove yavo nekunwa weti yavo pamwe nemwi?
\p
\v 13 Zvino Rabhi-Sheka wakamira ndokudana neinzwi guru muChiJudha, ndokuti: Inzwai mashoko amambo mukuru, mambo weAsiriya.
\v 14 Anoreva seizvi mambo: Hezekia Ngaarege kukunyengerai; nokuti haangagoni kukurwirai.
\v 15 Uye Hezekiya ngaarege kukuvimbisai naJehovha, achiti: Jehovha achatirwira zvirokwazvo; guta iri haringapiwi mumaoko amambo weAsiriya.
\v 16 Musateerera kuna Hezekia, nokuti anoreva seizvi mambo weAsiriya: Tsvakai nyasha kwandiri nechipo, mutumire kwandiri, mudye umwe neumwe zvemuzambiringa wake, uye umwe neumwe zvemuonde wake, umwe neumwe anwe mvura yetsime rake;
\v 17 kusvika pakusvika kwangu, ndikakuisai munyika yakafanana nenyika yenyu, nyika yezviyo newaini, nyika yechingwa neminda yemizambiringa.
\v 18 Zvimwe Hezekiya angakunyengetedzai achiti: Jehovha achatirwira. Vamwari vendudzi vakanunura here umwe neumwe nyika yake paruoko rwamambo weAsiriya?
\v 19 Varipi vamwari veHamati neAripadhi? Varipi vamwari vveSefarivhaimi? Vakarwira Samariya paruoko rwangu here?
\v 20 Ndiani pakati pavamwari vese venyika idzi vakanunura nyika yavo kubva muruoko rwangu kuti Jehovha angarwira Jerusarema kubva muruoko rwangu?
\v 21 Asi vakanyarara, uye havana kumupindura shoko; nokuti murairo wamambo waiti: Musamupindura.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Eriakimu mwanakomana waHirikiya, waiva pamusoro peimba, wakasvika kuna Hezekia, naShebhina munyori, naJoa mwanakomana waAsafi, munyori wenhoroondo, ndokubvarura nguvo dzavo, ndokumuudza mashoko aRabhi-Sheka.
